high_descs: Walk left around the table to the other side of it.
Pick up the pot on the table.
Turn right and veer right to the fridge.
Place the pot on the top shelf of the fridge. Close the door, wait a moment, and take it out again.
Turn around and walk a bit left, back to the close long side of the table.
Place the pot on the table in the front right corner.
anns.task_desc: Place a chilled pot on a table.

high_descs: Turn left and walk to the wall then turn right and walk past the green table then turn right and walk until you're even with the pan on the green table then turn right to face it.
Pick up the pan that's in front of you on the green table.
Turn right and walk to the wall then turn right.
Chill the pan in the fridge then get it back out and close the door.
Walk back to where you got the pan.
Put the pan on the green table way to the right of where you got it so it's above the two mugs under the table.
anns.task_desc: Put a cold pan on the tabel.

high_descs: Turn to your left and go to the wall, then turn to your right and go past the island, turn to your right again and turn towards the island in front of the metal bowl.
Pick up the metal bowl on the island.
Turn to your right, go to the wall then turn to the refrigerator on your right.
Place the bowl in the center of the top shelf of the refrigerator, wait a moment for the bowl to chill, then remove the bowl from the refrigerator.
Turn to your right and go to the sink, then turn to the island on your right.
Place the bowl on the right side of the kitchen island.
anns.task_desc: Put a chilled bowl on the kitchen island.
